Circle Assignment
Instructions
1. Tasks for Both Versions
In both versions of your test class, complete the following task:

Create three Circle objects, each with a different radius.


2. CircleTest02
In the class CircleTest02, make the following update:

Change the condition in the if statement so that it checks whether the radius is greater than 200.
Run your program and observe what changes in the output.


